               <interp inst="t17570420-41" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17570420"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17570420-41" type="date" value="17570420"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17570420-41-off210-c361" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570420-41-defend436 t17570420-41-off210 t17570420-41-verdict213"></join>
         
               <p>186. (L) 
               
                  <persName id="t17570420-41-defend436" type="defendantName">
                     Hannah 
                     Fordham 
                  <interp inst="t17570420-41-defend436" type="surname" value="Fordham"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570420-41-defend436" type="given" value="Hannah"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570420-41-defend436" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , <rs id="t17570420-41-deflabel209" type="occupation">spinster</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570420-41-defend436 t17570420-41-deflabel209"></join>, was indicted for <rs id="t17570420-41-off210" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17570420-41-off210" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570420-41-off210" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing one stuff gown, value 2 s. two linen aprons, value 2 s. one cloak, and one handkerchief
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17570420-41-victim438" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Hare 
                  <interp inst="t17570420-41-victim438" type="surname" value="Hare"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570420-41-victim438" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570420-41-victim438" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570420-41-off210 t17570420-41-victim438"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17570420-41-cd211" type="crimeDate">April 18</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570420-41-off210 t17570420-41-cd211"></join>.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17570420-41-person439">
                  John 
                  Hare 
               <interp inst="t17570420-41-person439" type="surname" value="Hare"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570420-41-person439" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570420-41-person439" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner came and offered herself to me as a <rs id="t17570420-41-deflabel212" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570420-41-defend436 t17570420-41-deflabel212"></join> on the 15th of April, and my wife hired her She rob'd me of the things mentioned in the indictment, went away, and left the door open; she was persued, and taken with them upon her. Produced in court, and deposed to.</p>

               <p>
                  <rs id="t17570420-41-verdict213" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17570420-41-verdict213" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17570420-41-punish214" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17570420-41-punish214" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570420-41-defend436 t17570420-41-punish214"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
